reviews.review_text: No mas! Last show in New Haven. Great, grubby little New England hockey arena. Really solid jamming this night, standout Birdsong, China/Rider, killer Other One w little Eleven hints at end jam! Phil dominated this one. Fun times. Freaks were pitting Wesson oil in the hallway corners to swirl around on!!
